dct_alternative_sm: From Isle Au Haut to Cape Cod
Isle Au Haut to Cape Cod
dct_description_sm: Bathymetry shown by soundings and isolines, relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Includes notes on buoys, tides, soundings and authorities.

Includes index on "Light Houses", "Latitude", "Longitude West from Greenwich Obervatory", "Character", "Time Between Flashes", "Height of light above sea level", "Distance visible in Naut. miles", "Order of lens", "Color of tower" and "Fog signals".
